    General description of IRS and LLINs interventions parameterizations

    interventions_param.Rd

    This data object contains a general description of all available IRS and LLIN intervention parameterizations.

    interventions_param

    Format

    A data frame with 7 columns consisting of:

    • Parameterisation: ID of the parameterization

    • Intervention: name identified of the intervention, can only take value "IRS", "LLINs" or "House screening"

    • Active agent: insecticide name

    • Species: name of the mosquito species

    • Reference: publication reference

    • Method: fitting method

    • Duration: duration until intervention renewal

    Value

    general intervention description
